data.description: Charming North Rural Hanford home, with easy access to CA-41 and CA-43 for easy commuting and traveling! Featuring 3 beds, 2 baths, spacious living spacious, and sizable backyard! Large living room greets you upon entry. Spacious dining room open to the kitchen. New laminate floors throughout! Sizable backyard boasts a storage shed, covered patio, and additional covered area for entertaining - can make potential carport. Make this turn-key ready home your oasis!
